data.text:
Unedited Description Supplied by Transferring Agency:

STATE VISIT OF PRESIDENT AND MRS S R NATHAN TO THAILAND - STATE BANQUET GIVEN BY THEIR MAJESTIES KING BHUMIBOL ADULYADEJ AND QUEEN SIRIKIT OF THAILAND AT CHAKRI THRONE HALL IN THE GRAND PALACE, BANGKOK

Description Edited by NAS:

Thai official and his wife being introduced to the Thai Royal Family, President and Mrs S R Nathan at state banquet given by Their Majesties King Bhumibol Adulyadej and Queen Sirikit of Thailand at Chakri Throne Hall in the Grand Palace, Bangkok. The Singapore President was on a five-day state visit to Thailand.
